{"tid":2208632,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都係因為楊千樺(人瑞)而忍痛唔睇麥路人？","createTime":"2020-09-19T05:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T17:10:23.000Z","uid":4322,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8cc6212f82078183a7e5f9606e59dc024faa0e","tid":2208632,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>麥路人個題材明明好正！你揀錯粒老鼠屎呀屌！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<ins>又有呀王同達明同萬子同鮑姐(hi 耆齡王)</ins><br />\n<br />\n先唔講人瑞佢奶共同唱歌唔好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢做戲真係唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢死人樣已經唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKqK6NZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKqK6NZ.png&h=66aa21f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔靚又無特色又無演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住會諗條八婆點解會拎過金像獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但Sammi竟然未拎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮喇人瑞 笑你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同 收皮喇人瑞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔認同 我愛人瑞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e88ee4295e8cdfaa21b4b6213f53bddf400e33","tid":2208632,"uid":4322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"認同！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a05c1d2311b2465ba260954982eb3d09faa6b80","tid":2208632,"uid":139720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05: